Opportunity Sight is an AI-powered Smart Market Entry Engine designed for manufacturers. It analyzes a factory’s location, resources, certifications, and market trends to recommend the most profitable new product categories and market opportunities. With personalized suggestions and a Trend Explorer that leverages live data through the Gemini API, the platform empowers businesses to diversify, minimize risk, and stay ahead of trends. Built with Lovable for seamless API integration and rapid prototyping, Opportunity Sight enables actionable, data-driven decisions through interactive dashboards—maximizing ROI and providing clear, practical guidance for manufacturing growth.